Title: Za'Tual
Description:
The Zandalari have been a constant nuisance since we arrived on this island. I've assigned Archmage Lan'dalock to take charge of dismantling their presence at Za'Tual, in the south.

Report to him when you are best able. He will have work for you.
ObjectivesText: Find Archmage Lan'dalock outside of Za'Tual.
RewardText: One more to join the Zandalari hunt?  Good.  Very good.
